commands para inicializar um projeto react

1 - yarn init - y (comando para criar o package.json)
2 - yarn add @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react webpack webpack-cli
 (comando para instalar as dependencias do webpack)
3 - yarn add react react-dom (instalar o react)
4 - yarn add babel-loader -D
5 - yarn add webpack-dev-server -D
6 - yarn add style-loader css-loader -D
7 - yarn add file-loader -D
8 - yarn add @babel/plugin-proposal-class-properties -D
9 - yarn add prop-types
